{"tid":2355603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本法第52條有無違反國安法？","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T11:17:11.000Z","uid":105567,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7993f4bacf364377ae5ef542c8a094637d795e7","tid":2355603,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"基本法第五十二條例明，如立法會否決財政預算案，重選的立法會亦繼續否決，行政長官就必須辭職。<br />\n<br />\n今日逾50名民主派初選人士被國安處以顛覆政權罪行大舉搜捕。國安處李桂華指否決財政預算案令行政長官辭職為「陰謀」，而保安局局長李家超則以「歹毒」形容。二人又指以上行為顛覆政權。"},{"pid":"32bb37f9c6200c50e550d2dcc58d1071f73ef0c4","tid":2355603,"uid":389214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"香港仲有基本法架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa75cb6dbe229700c48e802bf9ec26943c06f50a","tid":2355603,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"22條都冇左件事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b04b74d613ba4a94ce7381163928e5d2ea96d3","tid":2355603,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa75cb6dbe229700c48e802bf9ec26943c06f50a","tid":2355603,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"22條都冇左件事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200418-3020copy_S5iQU_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200418-3020copy_S5iQU_1200x0.png&h=033b8f4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40a02fa423b50f7e5d09657b895744fb242be528","tid":2355603,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa75cb6dbe229700c48e802bf9ec26943c06f50a","tid":2355603,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"repl